      "text": "2016 Archive Job seekers invited to Career Fair at NOVA-Loudoun \n  Loudoun Campus will host a free Career Fair on Tuesday, April 26 from 1 to 4 p.m. in the Higher Education Center.Job seekers are welcome to meet with more than 70 local employers hiring for full-time, part-time, seasonal and internship positions. The fair will showcase employment opportunities in childcare, education, local government, IT/computer science, mental health, fitness, healthcare, personal care, hospitality, retail, public safety, sales and skilled labor. NOVA-Loudoun is at 21200 Campus Drive in Sterling. Please park in student lots only. For more information, contact Laura Siko at . # # # \n ",
