      "title": "Traverse City West Senior High Hosts Job Fair",
      "text": "Traverse City West Senior High Hosts Job Fair Posted: Follow @dmlyden9and10 \nSome local high school students got a jump start on looking for a summer job. \nFor the past two nights, Traverse City West Senior High has hosted a job fair with local employers. \nIt gave students a chance to talk with them about open jobs and how to apply. \nSome employers also did interviews on site giving students the chance to go through the interview process in a relaxed atmosphere. \n“They can talk to a lot of different employers and find out the availability of what jobs are open in the community for the summer and that could potentially turn into a longer part time job planned for them,” said Kim Prisk, a business teacher at the school. \nMore than 1,600 students attended over the two days. Most Popular Stories Most Popular Stories More>>",
