      "title": "iQor’s Simi Valley Contact Center Seeking Over 150 Jobs to Support Major Media Client",
      "text": "April 29, 2016 at 15:39 PM EDT iQor’s Simi Valley Contact Center Seeking Over 150 Jobs to Support Major Media Client iQor’s Simi Valley Contact Center Seeking Over 150 Jobs to Support Major Media Client. Flexible Schedules, Competitive Pay and Work Class Development Program \niQor, a global provider of customer contact solutions and product support services, announced its contact center located in Simi Valley, California is seeking over 150 new customer service agents to support a major media client. Currently, the company is accepting applications on-line or in person. As an added bonus, after 90-days of employment iQor employees receive free Media service from the client! A $280 per month value! When Are We Hiring: Now Until the End of 2016 Who Are We Looking for: 150+ customer service call center agents \n(Competitive pay and flexible schedules including; multiple day and evening shifts. Inquire about our College Student shift schedules!) \nAgent Qualifications Needed: \nGreat attitude and goal oriented! Where Are We Located: iQor Simi Center of Excellence \n2290 Agate Court Unit A1 \nSimi Valley, CA 93065 Easily Apply from Any PC, Tablet or Mobile Device: \nInterested candidates may apply online using iQor’s mobile responsive application at \nhttps://eapt.iqor.com/ \n“Demand for our client’s services is at an all-time high. Our Simi Valley contact center plays a critical role in delivering high quality support,” said Tone Holmen, SVP, iQor Operations. “This latest request is a testament to our high performance culture. We’re looking for talented, goal oriented employees and have budgeted for very competitive wages, bonuses and free media services. There has never been a better time to join us.” \nAbout iQor \niQor is a global provider of customer interaction solutions and product support services with 35,000 employees in 18 countries. Our award-winning technology, logistics and analytics platforms enable us to measure, monitor, and analyze brand interactions, improve business processes, and find operational efficiencies that lead to superior outcomes for our partners across the customer and product lifecycles. For more information, please visit us at www.iqor.com or follow us at www.twitter.com/iqor . View source version on businesswire.com: http://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20160429006061/en/ Contacts:",
